<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.3.2">
<l>vacaiyil nāṉmaṟai keṭuttavam malarayaṟ karuḷimuṉ parimukamāy</l>
<l>icaikoḷ vētanū leṉṟivai payantava ṉēyeṉak karuḷpuriyē</l>
<l>yuyarkoḷ mātavip pōtoṭu lāviya mārutam vītiyiṉvāy</l>
<l>ticaiyel lāmkama ḻumpoḻil cūḻtiru veḷḷaṟai niṉṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Lord] who, once with a horse’s face, being gracious to unborn [Brahmā]</l>
<l rend="indent">on the lovely lotus who had lost</l>
<l>The four faultless Vedas, produced these saying,</l>
<l rend="indent">“[Here are] the Vedic texts which contain music,” grant me grace,</l>
<l>[Lord] who stands in Tiruveḷḷaṟai encircled by groves where the wind,</l>
<l rend="indent">which stirs in buds of high mādhavi vines,</l>
<l>Scents [the air] in all directions through the lanes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
